description: Large 1 bedroom condo located in the heart of South Beach with an amazing view of the Bay Bridge! This open concept floor plan has tons of natural light, 1 bath, in unit laundry, a private balcony, and a bonus room to boot that can be used as an office, yoga room or additional storage. Unit comes with 1 parking space and its own storage locker. Bridgeview is a full service building complete with 24 hour doorman, concierge, fitness center, heated pool and spa, and sky deck with BBQs and more spectacular views! With the Embarcadero, Ferry Building and farmer’s market a short distance from home, SF MOMA, Oracle Park and Chase Center around the way, Red’s Java House, the Hi-Dive, Water Bar and Epic Restaurant in the neighborhood, dog park and Salesforce Transit Center out your door, this place is not only close to transportation- bus, ferry, BART and freeway- it is conveniently located to everything!

description: Modern 15-unit building, fully upgraded loft with 200sqft private patio and common roof deck access. Newly refreshed kitchen with stainless appliances, upgraded bathrooms, and new flooring throughout. Truly a massive open living space with soaring walls is perfectly situated on the cusp of mid-Market, SoMa and FiDi. Near perfect transit blocks from MUNI, BART and seamless freeway! The addition of EV parking, central location and friendly neighbors make this the perfect place to call home.

description: Buena Vista Heights | SF: Live your bliss on a GRAND scale in this elegant + sophisticated VIEW home tucked conveniently across from SF's oldest public green space, Buena Vista Park.  With over 6,000 sqft this 4Br+Office / 4.5Ba estate-like residence carries a sumptuous nod towards Parisian architecture, newly built from the ground up in 2010 to create a modern haven of functionality + comfort. Engineered to transcend generations, this extraordinary home unfolds like a dreamy 5-Star' destination, brilliant with natural light, high ceilings & doors, majestic views spanning The City & Bay, enchanting indoor/outdoor spaces -- including terraced al-fresco' kitchen. Glamorous, high-end appointments, palatial breadth throughout. Hydraulic ELEVATOR. W/D. 2-Car garage pkg. Centrally located yet positioned high above the frenetic pace of The City. Minutes to Cole Valley, NoPa, Duboce Triangle, Castro, & Golden Gate Park. There's an exhilarating sense of living on top of the world' here.
